name: ux_design_system
version: "2.0.0"
language: zig
module: ux_design_system

description: |
  VIBEE Bot UI/UX Design System
  
  Based on Telegram Bot Best Practices:
  1. Progressive disclosure - show only relevant options
  2. Consistent navigation - always provide back/cancel
  3. Clear feedback - show progress and status
  4. Minimal cognitive load - group related actions
  5. Accessibility - support multiple languages
  6. Error recovery - graceful error handling
  7. Contextual help - inline tips and guidance

